 "title4_s9spyo2b4ke_html": "50K+",
 "text4_s9spyo2b4ke_html": "Satisfied Customers",
 "headingtext_8se9sdv2lio_html": "WE MAKE BEAUTIFUL <span style=\"color:#a70a10\">BUTCHERIES<\/span>",
 "textcontent_i2lgjnzp48_html": "A family business started from a butcher shop in Ibra, Oman, 1977- today <span style=\"font-weight:700\">we exist to nourish people with nature's finest red meat.<\/span>",
 "title0_jg8um1x1lbc_html": "3HRS <br>Delivery",
 "title1_jg8um1x1lbc_html": "Delivered <br>In A Box",
 "title2_jg8um1x1lbc_html": "Fresh & <br>Halal",
 "title0_hf45sa53dj4_html": "3HRS DELIVERY",
 "text0_hf45sa53dj4_html": "Fresh meat delivered within 3 <br> hours across Dubai",
 "title1_hf45sa53dj4_html": "DELIVERED IN A BOX",
 "text1_hf45sa53dj4_html": "Carefully packaged in an eco-<br>friendly, biodegradable box",
 "title2_hf45sa53dj4_html": "HORMONE FREE",
 "text2_hf45sa53dj4_html": "Free from Harmful Hormones&nbsp;<br>and Antibiotics&nbsp;",
 "title3_hf45sa53dj4_html": "FRESH & HALAL",
 "text3_hf45sa53dj4_html": "100% Halal &amp; Fresh meat for <br>you all day, everyday.",
 "headingtext_4wuyiozmvnc_html": "THE MLS EXPERIENCE ",
 "headingtext_053anuy3dnlf_html": "WHAT IS MLS?<span style=\"color:#a70a10\"><\/span>",
 "text0_ta1hyo9vzrh_html": "Fresh Meat Delivery: Economical to premium, all 100% fresh.\r\n",
 "text1_ta1hyo9vzrh_html": "Diverse Range: Locally sourced Emirati lamb to Australian Wagyu, under one roof.\r\n\r\n",
 "text2_ta1hyo9vzrh_html": "Quality Assurance: From grass-fed New Zealand beef to premium Australian lamb. ",
 "text3_ta1hyo9vzrh_html": "Dubai Expansion: Born in Oman during COVID-19, 15 stores strong, now heading to the UAE!",
 "buttoncontent_yi7zsy9kyyi_html": "LEARN MORE",
 "headingtext_mzu7wo1g65o_html": "FIRST <span style=\"background:#a70a10\">500 SUBSCRIBERS<\/span> <br>GET FREE SHIPPING<br> AND FREE MEAT!\n\n<span style=\"color:#a70a10\"><\/span>",
 "headingtext_n6jbb19c7s_html": "FIRST <span style=\"background:#a70a10\">500 SUBSCRIBERS<\/span> GET FREE SHIPPING AND FREE MEAT!\n\n<span style=\"color:#a70a10\"><\/span>",
 "textcontent_721nwv4ipik_html": "First 500 subscribers get <b style=\"color:#fff\">FREE SHIPPING, FREE NEW ZEALAND GRASS-FED BEEF RIBEYE STEAK 250GM X 1 &amp; FREE AUSTRALIAN BLACK ANGUS BEEF BURGERS 125GM X 2<\/b> with their first order.\n\u2028",
 "headingtext_8d9qtyub3v7_html": "MLS IS LOVED BY<br> 50K+ CUSTOMERS&nbsp;",
 "text0_wncctp98yrn_html": "\u201cExcellent experience MLS never fails to impress us thank you so much for the continuing follow up to ensure your clients are extremely happy \ud83d\ude0a\u201d",
 "name0_wncctp98yrn_html": "Noha R.",
 "title0_wncctp98yrn_html": "Verified Customer",
 "text1_wncctp98yrn_html": "\u201cMls burgers are delicious, you can feel and taste the meat, they have less fat than \"local Somali\" ones but they are more sturdy, I prefer them. The box offer...hats off!!!!\r\nIf I could give a million stars for the service and the people working I could. \r\nSpecial thanks to the guys in the Souq Al Madina! \u201d",
 "name1_wncctp98yrn_html": "Alice",
 "title1_wncctp98yrn_html": "Verified Customer",
 "text2_wncctp98yrn_html": "\u201cMLS has established a high bar and they know how to maintain it! delivery was prompt, with usual nice and clean product...\u201d",
 "name2_wncctp98yrn_html": "Muhammad A.",
 "title2_wncctp98yrn_html": "Verified Customer",
 "headingtext_x6ae1pu6n9h_html": "Drop us a line!",
